query:
WITH bounds AS (
                        SELECT *
                        FROM UNNEST($1::text[], $2::bigint[]) AS b(producer_name, above_id)
                    )
                    SELECT
                        m.message_id,
                        m.producer_name,
                        m.content_json,
                        m.occurred_on,
                        m.version as "version!"
                    FROM outbox_messages AS m
                    JOIN bounds AS b
                        ON m.producer_name = b.producer_name AND m.message_id > b.above_id
                    ORDER BY m.message_id
                    LIMIT $3
